19f1171b-bce0-4eec-8910-23c8b2edc3ba\">1월 즈음에, 금방 봄 되고 여름 되고 가을 되고 또 겨울이 오겠지? 했는데 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b28570f3-4d95-4880-8a60-b922e13ac98c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-73e9e8eb-2a8f-40be-bf49-4ef81aa514b0\">역시나 눈 깜짝할 사이에 금방 12월이 왔고 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-85d585bb-76f4-434c-beb5-57d530d60eb2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6abd4fea-5816-4eef-b9e2-a876369ecf1c\">벌써 크리스마스네요 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-edac286c-fc49-4b23-9b6f-2c201c781888\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bc996b5c-3016-4b8f-af78-b43d1111658f\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f5f3d566-18a6-4752-9763-b1f01c4b6687\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d6ec16e0-5583-4fc9-8696-037ff3f5e3dc\">한 해 동안 무탈하게 잘 지내셨나요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d283f2a8-af2a-432b-9439-b1f2ddec7e0d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ac790bb2-8565-4a86-bead-ecb6dd1e7f9c\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-86855806-991a-4c6d-9a34-712c0dbda38e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-